quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Inene esi siTyhilelo Sasityhila ngoBusuku baMandla
  97,2,Yintoni na enokukucacisela okokuba buyintoni na uBusuku baMandla
  97,3,UBusuku baMandla bungcono kuneenyanga eziliwaka
  97,4,"Ngabo kuhla iingelosi noMoya [oyiNgcwele (uJibrîl)] ngemvume ka-Allâh nemiyalelo yonke"
  97,5,(Ngobo busuku) kuba luxolo kude kube ngoms’obomvu